# Gemini API Key — required for AI analysis features in web/development mode.
# In the Electron desktop app, the API key is entered and persisted via the
# Settings page (stored in localStorage) — this .env file is not needed there.
#
# Get a free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
